# <a name="saving-messages-in-outlookcom"></a><span data-ttu-id="93c73-102">Spara meddelanden i Outlook.com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-102">Saving messages in Outlook.com</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93c73-103">Du kan spara e-postmeddelanden i Outlook.com, men du kan skriva ut dem på en PDF-fil som du kan spara på din dator.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-103">You cannot save email messages in Outlook.com, but you can print them to a PDF which you can save on your PC.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93c73-104">Verktyget Microsoft skriva ut till PDF som ingår i Windows 10 kan du skriva ut ett e-postmeddelande direkt till en PDF-fil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-104">The Microsoft Print To PDF utility included in Windows 10 allows you to print any email message directly to a PDF.</span></span>

1. <span data-ttu-id="93c73-105">Markera det meddelande som du vill spara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-105">Select the message you want to save.</span></span>
2. <span data-ttu-id="93c73-106">Välj tre punkter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-106">Select the three dots</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="93c73-107">överst i meddelandet och välj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-107">at the top of the message and then select</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="93c73-108">**Skriv ut**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-108">**Print**.</span></span>
3. <span data-ttu-id="93c73-109">Välj **Skriv ut** igen och välj **Microsoft Print till PDF**på skrivare-menyn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-109">Select **Print** again, and from the printer drop-down menu, select **Microsoft Print to PDF**.</span></span>
4. <span data-ttu-id="93c73-110">Välj **Skriv ut**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93c73-110">Select **Print**.</span></span>
